NFO Viewer 1.7
==============

 [D] Add menu item to toggle line-wrapping
 [D] Automatically switch to wrapping lines if a line longer than
     160 characters is found in the file (the threshold is
     customizable in the configuration file)
 [D] Fix URL-detection to be less strict
 [D] Fall back to 'monospace' if preferred font is not found
 [D] Add Italian translation (Alessio Treglia)

